      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant with individual throttle bodies and a signature 8,000 RPM redline. Power is routed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, ensuring exceptional corner-exit traction. This chassis has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive Vanos system refresh and structural subframe reinforcement to mitigate common floor-pan fatigue. The suspension retains its telepathic feedback thanks to refreshed control arm bushings and performance-tuned dampers. While the exterior shows light patina consistent with a well-loved enthusiast machine, the mechanical synchronization and compression across all six cylinders remain within tight tolerances. It is a mechanically robust specimen ready for spirited B-road duty.",
